# 4. predator species, 0=no, 1=VPA predator, 2=Other predator 
# 5. prey species, 0=no, 1=yes
# 6. Spawning season (not used yet, but set to 1)
# 7. Additional data1
# 8. additional data2
# 9. additional data3
##
